import { Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap';

function FilterComponent() {
  return (
    <Row>
      <Col md={9}>
        <Col md={2}>
          <input />
        </Col>
        <Col md={2}>
          <input />
        </Col>
        <Col md={2}>
          <input />
        </Col>
        <Col md={2}>
          <input />
        </Col>
        <Col md={2}>
          <input />
        </Col>
      </Col>
      <Col md={3}></Col>
    </Row>
  );
}

export default FilterComponent;
